text: Sybra biguttula is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1964.BioLib.cz - Sybra biguttula. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. It contains two subspecies, Sybra biguttula biguttula and Sybra biguttula samarensis. ==References== biguttula Category:Beetles described in 1964
title: Sybra biguttula
